        Compares the LocalizedString slugs of a ShoppingList and a ShoppingListDraft and returns an UpdateAction<ShoppingList> as a result in an Optional. If both the ShoppingList and the ShoppingListDraft have the same slug, then no update action is needed and hence an empty Optional is returned.

        oldShoppingList - the shopping list which should be updated.
        newShoppingList - the shopping list draft where we get the new slug.
